settings.title: MEET YOUR NEW BEDTIME BFF
settings.text:
Klova ZPatches combine melatonin and all natural ingredients in a convenient transdermal patch.

Simply apply about an hour before bed to start unwinding, and ease into deep, restorative sleep. Clinically Proven, natural ingredients in the ZPatch are absorbed throughout the night, and can help keep you sleeping soundly for up to 8 hours. The Best Part? No groggy mornings. 94% of Customers Surveyed said they actually woke up MORE refreshed, with MORE energy, following nights where they used the ZPatch. Try them Hassle Free - thanks to our 30 Day Money Back Guarantee.

settings.title: How it works
settings.text:
Our unique, transdermal ingredient delivery technology is what makes the ZPatch the highest rated sleep patch in the country.

The Contact Layer of the Patch is infused with Cosmoperine, a black pepper extract that prepares the skin for absorption by opening up the upper dermis capillaries. Within 20 - 60 minutes of putting on a ZPatch, your skin starts to absorb the all natural ingredients from the Formula Layer of the Patch. These ingredients are absorbed for about 6 hours, so they wear off before you rise - leaving you rested, refreshed, energized and ready to take on the day.

settings.title: How To Use It
settings.text:
Using the ZPatch is easy

You can place it just about anywhere, but most users prefer the top of foot, shoulder, abdomen, calf or forearm. The ideal location is a clean, hairless part of the body. Even ‘peachfuzz’ can affect the ingredient delivery, so we recommend shaving the area it will be placed, especially if there is a little body hair. Simply Peel off a patch, Stick it on, and you’ll start to feel the effects within 20-60 minutes. Discard the patch in the morning, and remove any of the excess, natural adhesive with soap, water or rubbing alcohol. (Shaving the area prior to use prevents excess adhesive sticking to skin when patch is removed in the morning)
